==Russian==
[[Category:Russian nouns]]

===Etymology===
From [[Tatar]] баклак

===Noun===
'''баклага''' (baklága) {{f}}, баклаги (baklági) {{p}}<br>
''also colloq.'' [[баклажка]]

# a type of [[flask]] for carrying liquids with [[hook]]s on the sides for [[strap]]s
# (''colloq.'') any [[flask]] for carrying liquids

